1
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,620
During the Great Ming era,

2
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:47,120
relations between China and Siam flourished.

3
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,680
Siam sent envoys to propose a marriage alliance,

4
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:52,539
and the Great Ming granted a princess for the union.

5
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,759
This cross-ocean alliance

6
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,840
was ostensibly a legendary tale

7
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,640
of securing borders, fostering relations,

8
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:01,600
and building peace together.

9
00:02:02,240 --> 00:02:03,280
However, behind it,

10
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:06,480
lay a thousand-year-old secret of the Zhuang ancestors.

11
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:10,199
Legend has it that four totem bronze frogs,

12
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,360
once gathered,

13
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:15,120
can summon the divine artifact capable of extending life

14
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,600
and stabilizing the nation,

15
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,840
Buluotuo's Tear.

16
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:24,340
Various factions coveted the bronze frogs and the holy artifact.

17
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:27,840
A battle of light and shadow across mountains and seas

18
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,040
begins now.

19
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,960
What a pretty little mouth.

20
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,400
Is this the Princess?

21
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:07,000
She must be even more beautiful than a goddess.

22
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,160
Have a grape.

23
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:16,020
No? I'll eat it myself.

24
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,280
The orange is delicious.

25
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:28,800
Have a banana.

26
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,460
This banana

27
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,380
is super sweet.

28
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:51,370
Don't look at me. Look at the knife.

29
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,720
I am the real Princess Zhaoyang.

30
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,560
Someone took advantage while I was unconscious

31
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,480
to swap me out.

32
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:27,360
I knew something was off with that Princess.

33
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,480
Who on earth wants to harm me?

34
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,600
How should I know?

35
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,560
Think carefully about how you

36
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,490
usually behave.

37
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,520
Where is the army?

38
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,260
What did you say? I can't hear you.

39
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,520
I said,

40
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:17,240
Prince, where is your army?

41
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,680
My army has arrived.

42
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:28,400
Th-this... Is this your army?

43
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,880
Hand over the Buluotuo Tear,

44
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,340
and I'll spare your lives.

45
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,240
Never.

46
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,400
Fight our way out.

47
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,640
Prince,

48
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:22,770
can't you be useful?

49
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,160
W-What did I do?

50
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:25,720
Hand over Buluotuo's Tear.

51
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,480
Never.
